body_html:
What do you mean when you say "I can install it with a previous version?"

Are you building from the 0.4 branch or master?

Could you try cleaning with the following:

  • pip uninstall torch
  • pip uninstall torch (yes, twice)
  • "python setup.py clean" and rebuilding?

body:
What do you mean when you say "I can install it with a previous version?"

Are you building from the 0.4 branch or master?

Could you try cleaning with the following:
- pip uninstall torch
- pip uninstall torch (yes, twice)
- "python setup.py clean" and rebuilding?
